README for Power API Application-level Power Monitoring and Control Demo Source

To build:
1) Ensure the Power API environment is loaded
    > module load powerapi
2) Type `make`
    > make


To execute:
1) Choose the OMP_NUM_THREADS you'd like and export (optional)
    > export OMP_NUM_THREADS=12
2) Launch pwrdemo on a single compute node
    > [launcher] [launcher options] ./pwrdemo [pwrdemo options]
